if we use wikidata, we should follow their best practices:
https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Wikidata:Data_access#Best_practices_to_follow

wikidata has specific requirements for using scripts:
https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/API:Cross-site_requests

introduction to wikidata:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m_9_23jXPoE

wikidata api sandbox:
https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:ApiSandbox#action=wbgetentities&format=json&origin=*&ids=Q79015&languages=en

for searching:
https://www.wikidata.org/w/api.php?action=help&modules=wbsearchentities

for accessing dynamic json data:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11922383/how-can-i-access-and-process-nested-objects-arrays-or-json/11922384#11922384

